lead_paragraph: Michael Brantley was 4 for 5 with three RBIs, Mike Napoli hit a three-run homer and the Cleveland Indians beat the Detroit Tigers for the sixth straight time this season, 9-4 on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Brantley, Napoli Lead Indians to Sweep of Tigers, 9-4
